				<p>My last job before this was as a Product Manager at Kickstarter. I worked on <a href="http://www.kickstarter.com/discover/advanced"> a new set of Discovery tools</a> amongst other things. A big part of working at Kickstarter is getting to see (and support!) creative projects. Here are a few projects I recently backed:</p>
